# Data Directory

This directory contains all site content as JSON files:

- recipes.json - All recipe data
- posts.json - All blog posts and stories
- lexicon.json - Baking lexicon entries
- books.json - Reading list items
- playlists.json - Playlist data

These files are managed by:
1. Sveltia CMS (at /admin)
2. Custom editors (admin-content.html, admin-playlists.html)

Both commit changes directly to GitHub.
